name: The Instrument of Birth
description:
This is the beginning of the story, and still a mystery. The first queen of god; AZALEA, lives in the void space that she created called JAGADJIGO. One day she decided to divide herself, manifesting her Dzat into the trinity of god that we know; MVDRA, SVNYA, and KVLLA. They were created with Insecta combined with Dzat Azalea.

Mvdra is the firstborn, he was born from Dzat moth. Svnya is the second and Kvlla is the third born. Azalea manifests herself and also her mind into this trinity, and lets them have their own consciousness and control. This trinity of god must seek the purpose of their birth and why Azalea split herself.

1080x1350 px
